source.name: Vacation And Sick Day Comparison
source.description: Comparison of vacation and sick days portion of the employee benefits package. The overall data is based on policy and statue for the current fiscal year. The market estimate for sick days/leave is based on the 2011 Towers Watson Survey General Industry Benefit Policies and Practices Survey Report.
